  "detailed_description": "<strong>TINY VISITORS</strong> is a <strong>3D Platformer</strong>, based on <strong>physics</strong>, mixing <strong>escape-game</strong>, <strong>search&find</strong> and <strong>mini-games</strong>. You can play up to <strong>4 players</strong> in local coop.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446070/extras/6fc27b18c1833eb9cf51331d9e560576.avif?t=1688028254\" width=553 height=162 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3D Platformer</h2>You can (and you'll have to) run, jump, climb, use a jetpack, fall, fall and use your jetpack, fall again, ragequit, jump again... I think you got it !<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446070/extras/e539f692a534ac74b1029ffea8b22856.avif?t=1688028254\" width=553 height=162 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics</h2>Grab, pull, push, throw all small objects around you. The lighter it is, the faster it flies. Have fun using objects to help your friends reaching high skies !<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446070/extras/df7cbb9671d254428072ea3c3c00c053.avif?t=1688028254\" width=553 height=162 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Local coop up to 4 players</h2>You don't have to go alone in the adventure. Play with your friends ! (if you have more than 3 friends, don't waste your time on this game, go play outside)<br>Help each other or mess with one another.<br>(Some controllers are needed for local multiplayer)<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2446070/extras/4dc2fc1023bbac0db1b691901a17181b.avif?t=1688028254\" width=553 height=162 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mini-games</h2>You're tired of searching a way to escape the house ? Take a break with funny mini-games you'll find in the rooms.",
